OL,7,FThe chancellor has been saying
OL,8,Fpublicly for several months that he
OL,9,Fwants to lower the tax burden.
OL,11,FITV News' Political Editor Robert
OL,12,FPeston has confirmed that Mr Hunt is
OL,13,Fset to knock two per cent off the rate
OL,14,Fof employee national insurance in his
OL,15,FBudget.
