OL,7,FThe chancellor will repeat his view
OL,8,Fthat countries with lower taxes are
OL,9,Fmore economically dynamic (although
OL,10,Fthe evidence for this is mixed) and
OL,11,Fthat he is delivering a "Budget for
OL,12,FLong Term Growth".
OL,14,FBut if there wasn't an election months
OL,15,Faway, would he really be cutting taxes
OL,16,Fnow?
