OL,7,FOr, as the International Monetary Fund
OL,8,F(IMF) did put it in January: it would
OL,9,Fbe unwise for the British government
OL,10,Fto cut taxes now. Indeed, taxes
OL,11,Farguably need to rise.
OL,13,FAre the chancellor's tax cuts credible?
OL,15,FThe chancellor promises he will only
OL,16,Fcut taxes in a "responsible and
OL,17,Fprudent" way.
