OL,7,FReducing the main rate of National
OL,8,FInsurance will be a welcome tax break
OL,9,Ffor anyone in work but the cut is
OL,10,F"regressive" in the sense that high
OL,11,Fearners enjoy the biggest benefit.
OL,13,FAllowing people to hold on to more of
OL,14,Ftheir earnings does provides an
OL,15,Fincentive to work at a time when the
OL,16,Fnumber of people who are "economically
OL,17,Finactive" is high.
