OL,7,FAnd cutting the main rate of Income
OL,8,FTax would have been more expensive and
OL,9,Fmore regressive. It would also have
OL,10,Fbeen a tax break for pensioners and
OL,11,Flandlords, who don't pay national
OL,12,Finsurance.
OL,14,FOn the face of it, the chancellor
OL,15,Fcan't really afford a big election
OL,16,Fgiveaway.
OL,18,FThere has been a lot of talk about
OL,19,F"headroom" in recent weeks.
