OL,7,FThat's tight.
OL,9,FChancellors have held an average
OL,10,Fbuffer of #29 billion against their
OL,11,Ffiscal rules since 2010.
OL,13,FCutting national insurance will eat-up
OL,14,F#10 billion of the chancellor's
OL,15,Fheadroom.
OL,17,FFreezing Fuel Duty again, which the
OL,18,Fchancellor will also do in his Budget,
OL,19,Fburns through another #4 billion.
OL,21,FThat's his headroom gone.
