OL,7,FHow will tax cuts be paid for?
OL,9,FThe chancellor doesn't have the
OL,10,F"headroom" to fund a two per cent cut
OL,11,Fto National Insurance so he intends to
OL,12,Fcreate it.
OL,14,FOne way in which he will do this is by
OL,15,Fscraping together a number of smaller
OL,16,Ftax rises elsewhere.
