OL,7,FTreasury sources have been briefing
OL,8,Fthat that Mr Hunt is looking squeezing
OL,9,Fmore out of "non-doms" - foreign
OL,10,Fnationals who are resident in the UK
OL,11,Fand have significant wealth overseas.
OL,13,FHe is also looking at higher taxes on
OL,14,FNorth Sea oil and gas production;
OL,15,Fvaping and tobacco; Airbnb/holiday
OL,16,Flets; and Air Passenger Duty for
OL,17,FBusiness travellers.
