OL,7,FPublic services are already under
OL,8,Fgreat pressure. Local authorities are
OL,9,Fgetting into financial difficulty. A
OL,10,Fhandful of councils have effectively
OL,11,Fgone bust, others are dimming
OL,12,Fstreetlights, leaving potholes
OL,13,Funfilled and turning down swimming
OL,14,Fpool heaters in an attempt to cut
OL,15,Fcosts.
