OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FHe chose not to use the windfall to
OL,8,Fhelp public services, where high
OL,9,Finflation has put pressure on budgets.
OL,11,FPut another way, Mr Hunt financed
OL,12,Flower taxes by squeezing public
OL,13,Fspending. And the signs are he is
OL,14,Fabout to do so again.
OL,16,FIn his Budget, the chancellor looks
OL,17,Fset to cut the planned growth rate in
OL,18,Foverall public spending (RDEL) from
OL,19,F0.9 per cent to 0.75 per cent from
OL,20,F2025/26 onwards.
