OL,4,Cquestions answered ahead of Hunt's
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FAs things stand, the Institute for
OL,8,FFiscal Studies (IFS) estimates the
OL,9,Fbudgets of unprotected departments -
OL,10,Flocal government, the courts, prisons
OL,11,Fand HMRC - will require cash top-ups
OL,12,Fof #20 billion a year by 2028/29 to
OL,13,Favoid funding cuts.
OL,15,FThe Budget is likely to increase the
OL,16,Fscale of the cuts which are currently
OL,17,Fpenciled in.
OL,19,FWill the tax cuts have to be reversed?
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G17/35
