OL,7,FThe chancellor's tax cuts are definite
OL,8,Fand certain, they will be implemented.
OL,10,FThe same cannot be said for his
OL,11,Fimplied spending cuts, because the
OL,12,Fgovernment has not yet done a spending
OL,13,Freview. And there has to be some doubt
OL,14,Fas to how realistic they are.
