OL,7,FIt is possible that Mr Hunt will stand
OL,8,Fup tomorrow and say "I have cuts taxes
OL,9,Ftoday because I think it is the right
OL,10,Fthing to do but that means I have had
OL,11,Fto make some tough choices. And I have
OL,12,Fdecided to make the following
OL,13,Fsacrifices..."
OL,15,FBut that's unlikely.
OL,17,FMr Hunt will instead speak of "more
OL,18,Fproductive public services."
