OL,7,FHe will set out his belief that the
OL,8,Fsolution here is not more money but
OL,9,Fgreater efficiency and he has a point.
OL,11,FThe NHS has more doctors and nurse
OL,12,Fthan it had before the pandemic and
OL,13,Fyet they are not doing more stuff, as
OL,14,Ffar as can be measured.
OL,16,FIt's not clear why productivity in the
OL,17,FNHS in England and Scotland has
OL,18,Fcollapsed in the way it has but it
OL,19,Fneeds addressing.
