OL,9,Fhave a lot of staff but they have
OL,10,Ffewer beds and much less diagnostic
OL,11,Fequipment (MRI, CT and PET scanners)
OL,12,Fthat in most other wealthy countries.
OL,14,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
