OL,3,CHow will tax cuts impact you? Nine
OL,4,Cquestions answered ahead of Hunt's
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FThe "tax burden" (tax receipts as a
OL,8,Fshare of Gross Domestic Product (GDP))
OL,9,Fin the UK is currently high by
OL,10,Fhistorical standards but it remains
OL,11,Fbelow the average across other
OL,12,Fadvanced economies.
OL,14,FTaxes have risen sharply since 2018,
OL,15,Fpartly to help pay for the #373
OL,16,Fbillion the government has spent
OL,17,Fhelping households and businesses
OL,18,Fendure two huge economic shocks since
OL,19,F2020, the pandemic, followed by
OL,20,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine.
