OL,3,CHow will tax cuts impact you? Nine
OL,4,Cquestions answered ahead of Hunt's
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FThe Furlough Scheme alone cost #69
OL,8,Fbillion.
OL,10,FAs it stands, the tax burden is on
OL,11,Fcourse to have risen by 4.2 per cent
OL,12,Fof GDP during the course of this
OL,13,Fparliament (2019 - 2024).
OL,15,FTo avoid this being "the biggest tax
OL,16,Fraising parliament ever" the
OL,17,Fchancellor will be need to bring taxes
OL,18,Fdown by 2.9 per cent of GDP in his
OL,19,FBudget, which feels impossible.
