OL,7,FBut a tax cut of 0.5 per cent of GDP
OL,8,Fmay be enough to keep the tax burden
OL,9,Fbelow the 1948 record (37.8 per cent
OL,10,Fof GDP).
OL,12,FWhat will tax cuts mean for interest
OL,13,Frates?
OL,15,FTax cuts put more money into people's
OL,16,Fpockets and create demand in the
OL,17,Feconomy.
