OL,3,CHow will tax cuts impact you? Nine
OL,4,Cquestions answered ahead of Hunt's
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FThe Bank of England is currently
OL,8,Ftrying to subdue demand by holding
OL,9,Finterest rates at a level that's high
OL,10,Fenough to get inflation back down to
OL,11,Ftarget.
OL,13,FIt's not obvious that now is a good
OL,14,Ftime for a major tax cut - 20 million
OL,15,Fpeople pay national insurance -
OL,16,Fbecause it is likely to put upward
OL,17,Fpressure on prices.
OL,19,FIt will be interesting to see how
OL,20,Finflationary the OBR thinks another 2
OL,21,Fpence off National Insurance is.
