OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FThis is a question that almost nobody
OL,8,Foutside Westminster will be asking
OL,9,Ftomorrow, or indeed perhaps ever.
OL,11,FThere is no academic consensus of what
OL,12,Fthe sensible level of debt as a share
OL,13,Fof national income should be.
OL,15,FBut Liz Truss's Mini Budget in
OL,16,FSeptember 2022 showed us what happens
OL,17,Fwhen international investors start to
OL,18,Fperceive the government as higher risk.
OL,20,FFiscal rules are designed to matter.
