OL,7,FThe objective of having debt falling
OL,8,Fin the medium term is perfectly
OL,9,Fsensible but his "rule" requires it to
OL,10,Fbe falling five years from when the
OL,11,FBudget is delivered.
OL,13,FThat "headroom" target is really
OL,14,Fsensitive. Small movements in the
OL,15,Fforecast can cause the numbers to move
OL,16,Fall over the show.
