OL,4,Cquestions answered ahead of Hunt's
OL,5,CBudget
OL,7,FMr Hunt will use his Budget to
OL,8,Fposition the Tories as the "low tax"
OL,9,Fparty that will allow you to hold onto
OL,10,Fmore of your earnings.
OL,12,FIt is also possible that he will also
OL,13,Fnick two of Labour's flagship
OL,14,Fmanifesto pledges: higher taxes for
OL,15,F"non-doms" and North Sea oil and gas
OL,16,Fproducers.
OL,18,FTo avoid being characterised as "tax
OL,19,Frisers," Labour may decide it needs to
OL,20,Fvote to support this Budget.
